{"tid":2368552,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求推介：家用鏡頭睇住老人家","createTime":"2021-01-16T09:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T16:02:54.000Z","uid":28402,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e836243313304270838b305bf74014e3b0ac553b","tid":2368552,"uid":28402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T09:48:11.000Z","msg":"屋企有個老人家，我番工時間無辦法睇住佢，想裝個屋企用的鏡頭（cctv) 間中睇下佢是否平安。<br />\n<br />\n我對cctv 完全無概念，想問連登仔有無咩牌子或型號推薦。<br />\n<br />\n條件大概如下：<br />\n<br />\n1）鏡頭要夠闊，屋企大約400尺。另外，有咩方法可以睇埋廚房/廁所？<br />\n<br />\n2）如果個cam 可用埋乾電就最好。因為屋企有些地方未必有足夠電製 support 個cam，也不想太多電線。<br />\n<br />\n先謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8edeca3bf764ed2e2a836fa98ae4013bbf7020","tid":2368552,"uid":265499,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T09:49:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59a1165e967e8695c9fa6e47d3084d863cdd26ff","tid":2368552,"uid":78336,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bd8edeca3bf764ed2e2a836fa98ae4013bbf7020","tid":2368552,"uid":265499,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T09:49:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T09:50:44.000Z","msg":"仲有免費雲備份同專人監察"},{"pid":"511385e0d97bbc8fb8a49b253dc65dcd6da184b0","tid":2368552,"uid":15659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T09:52:31.000Z","msg":"Arlo Pro 2<br />\n買兩三隻，可以行差電<br />\nSet up 方便，用 app 睇<br />\n有錄映功能"},{"pid":"602cc6c29e1fbeb0c08adafbdc2414636c619a46","tid":2368552,"uid":80139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T09:55:14.000Z","msg":"Arlo <br />\n用緊唔錯<br />\n不過一定貴過嗰啲支那小米"},{"pid":"af0c166aa9a77ffb31dcbf95d4785b9bb3f329f3","tid":2368552,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59a1165e967e8695c9fa6e47d3084d863cdd26ff","tid":2368552,"uid":78336,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bd8edeca3bf764ed2e2a836fa98ae4013bbf7020","tid":2368552,"uid":265499,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-